videos.description: Quade Green hits a 3-pointer in the side pocket for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Green swishes 3-pointer

videos.description: Tyree Crump finds Rayshaun Hammonds, who spins through the Kentucky defense and scores off the glass for the Bulldogs.
videos.headline: Georgia's Crump, Hammonds hook up for fast-break layup

videos.description: Jordan Harris feeds Rayshaun Hammonds, who finishes with a left-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Georgia's Harris, Hammonds connect for transition dunk

videos.description: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander intercepts a pass from Georgia and finds Quade Green for an easy layup.
videos.headline: Kentucky backcourt connects for an open-floor layup

videos.description: Wenyen Gabriel hits a 3-pointer from the top of the key off the dish from Shai Gilgeous-Alexander to extend the lead for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Kentucky executes pick-and-pop for 3-pointer

videos.description: John Calipari says he will use this win against Georgia as a teaching moment for his team.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Calipari: 'We got lucky and we got selfish today') 2017/12/31

videos.headline: Calipari: 'We got lucky and we got selfish today'

videos.description: Behind a game-high 21 points from Shai Gilgeous-Alexander, No. 16 Kentucky defeats Georgia 66-61.
videos.headline: Kentucky edges past Georgia
